name: OET Report TT
query:
SELECT
posting_date as "Posting Date::120",
title as "MTCN::120",
sender_name as "Send From::120",
receiver_name as "To::120",
amount_send as "Amount Send::120",
sender_currency as "Send Currency::120",
exchange_rate as "Exchange Rate::120",
amount_received as "Amount Received::120",
received_currency as "Received Currency::120",
purpose as "Purpose::120"
FROM `tabReceived TT`
